EFF supporters marched in their hundreds to pay
their last respects to a woman they called the "Mother of the
Nation."Members of the EFF gathered at Orlando Stadium on
Tuesday 3 April in Orlando, Soweto, and marched to the house of Winnie
Madikizela-Mandela. Mama Winnie, as she has come to be known, died on
